    "Secondly, the graph convolutional function is optimized in single-relational feature convolution channels to reduce oversmoothing and over-fitting.",
    "Then, residual connections with information interactions within and between channels are added to deepen the network.",
    "And finally, attention mechanism is employed to aggregate different relational features.",
    "DeepMCGCN addresses limitations in existing GCNs by introducing a multi-channel graph convolution mechanism, enabling more effective capture of diverse information within the graph.",
    "This helps to improve the model's ability to represent graph structures and node features, thereby enhancing performance and overcoming some of the limitations of current GCNs.Briefly, contributions are as follows:1."
